Raw salmon
Type: Material
Value: 2
Fine Value: 15
Keyword: Fish
Properties:
Bankable:     Droppable:
Sellable:     Tradable:

With its succulent and buttery flesh, salmon delights the palate with its rich and velvety texture.

The Raw salmon item is a material.
